description: CreAsian Food is redefining the idea of Japanese/Chinese fusion on a food truck. Offering delicious small plate items such as Tobiko Fish Balls to a fancy affordable seared Ahi Tuna Salad to a mouth watering house special Spicy CreAsian Chicken, CreAsian uses only the freshest ingredients and spices. Whether you are in the mood for a snack or hungry for a full meal, you won't be disappointed!
name: CreAsian
